query 'CALL graphql::explain("query { transactions(where: { blockNumber_gt: 100 }, first: 5) { hash from } }")'
---
> +-------+----------+---------------------+
> |  idx  |   kind   |       detail        |
> +-------+----------+---------------------+
> |   0   |   From   |    transactions     |
> |   1   |  Filter  |  blockNumber > 100  |
> |   2   |   Take   |          5          |
> |   3   |   Map    |     hash, from      |
> +-------+----------+---------------------+
>
